item.name: Program_Module_EndTOEnd

request.description:
This POST request creates a new program with following fields

Mandatory Fields : programName , programStatus

Autogenerated : programID ,creationTime, lastModTime

Post request sent with {{baseUrl}}/saveprogram.

**Pre-request Script:**

_var random_proname="Jun23-HugsForBugs-SDET-"+pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$randomInt}}');__pm.environment.set("Program_Name",random_proname);_

**Test:**

_pm.test("status code is 201: Created",()=>{_

_pm.response.to.have.status(201)});__var jsonData=JSON.parse(responseBody);_

_pm.globals.set("programId_env",jsonData.programId);_

_pm.globals.set("progName_env",jsonData.programName);_

_**Note : program description and program status were retrieved from CSV file while running collection so you couldnt see values in example**_

Expected result: 201: created

Actual: 202 created

**Negative scenario check** : creating a program with already existed program name which gives 400 bad request

**Tests:**

_pm.test("status code is 400:program name exists",()=>{ pm.response.to.have.status(400)});_

Expected result : Status code 400 bad request

Actual result: Status code 400 bad request

response.name: ProgramName_Exists

positive scenario : Request to retrieve all programs list

Endpoint :/allPrograms

**Tests:**

_pm.test("status code is 200:ok",()=>{_

_pm.response.to.have.status(200)});_

Expected result : Status code 200 ok

Actual result: Status code 200 ok

_pm.test("status code is 201: Created",()=>{_

_pm.response.to.have.status(201)});__var jsonData=JSON.parse(responseBody);_

_pm.globals.set("programId_env",jsonData.programId);_

_pm.globals.set("progName_env",jsonData.programName);_

_**Note : program description and program status were retrieved from CSV file while running collection so you couldnt see values in example**_

request.description:
This POST request creates a new program with following fields

Mandatory Fields : programName , programStatus

Autogenerated : programID ,creationTime, lastModTime

Post request sent with {{baseUrl}}/saveprogram.

**Pre-request Script:**

_var random_proname="Jun23-HugsForBugs-SDET-"+pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$randomInt}}');__pm.environment.set("Program_Name",random_proname);_

**Test:**

pm.test("status code is 201: Created",()=>{ pm.response.to.have.status(201)});  
var jsonData=JSON.parse(responseBody);

pm.globals.set("programId_env",jsonData.programId);

pm.globals.set("progName_env",jsonData.programName);pm.globals.set("time_env",jsonData.creationTime);

_**Note : program description and program status were retrieved from CSV file while running collection so you couldnt see values in example**_

Expected result: 201: created

Actual: 201 created

request.description:
**Testcase**: Create a new assignment submission

**Pre-request Script:**

let moment = require('moment');  
pm.variables.set('subDate', moment().add(2,'days').utc().format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss'));  
pm.variables.set('gradedDate', moment().add(7,'days').utc().format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss'));

**Tests:**

pm.test("Status code is 201:created", function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201);});var jsonData9=JSON.parse(responseBody);pm.globals.set("subId_env",jsonData9.submissionId);  
pm.globals.set("UserID",jsonData9.userId);

**Expected result:**

201 created

**Actual result:** 201 created

Note: We generated two different example responses

1. generates 400 bad request if submitted date is post due date
2. success record submission
    

_**BUG REPORT**_

1. _**Submission date is generating current date automatically though we are passing required value**_
2. _**gradedate time,grade and gradeby are giving null values in response though we are passing values in request body.**_

item.description:
This module works on submissions of assignments with fields like submission date,grading date and giving grades.

**Note:**

**we are facing many issues while working with assignment module.**

1. **Though the AssignmentID is available it says 404:not found.testcases are failing. we tried to capture all**
2. **Submission date is taking current date though we are passing the date from request.**
3. **grade,grade time,grade by giving null values in response, though we are passing correct values in the request**
    

**Due to this mainy testcases are failing.**
